Privacy Policy for ReiBot


Introduction

ReiBot is an AI-powered Discord bot designed to interact with users and improve its responses by learning from conversations within Discord servers.

By using ReiBot, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

Information Processed

ReiBot may process messages sent in channels where it is active in order to generate responses and improve its conversational abilities.

The bot does not intentionally collect personal information such as real names, addresses, phone numbers, or payment information.

How Information Is Used

Message content may be used to:

Generate responses to users.
Improve ReiBot's conversational performance.
Learn patterns of language and communication.
Maintain context during conversations.
Data Storage

ReiBot is designed to minimize data collection.

If message content is stored for learning purposes, it is stored only as necessary to improve the bot's functionality.

Data Sharing

ReiBot does not sell, rent, or share user data with third parties except when required by law.

User Responsibility

Users should avoid sharing sensitive personal information with ReiBot, including:

Passwords
Financial information
Government identification numbers
Private personal details
Data Removal

Server owners or users may contact the bot owner to request deletion of any stored data associated with ReiBot, where technically feasible.

Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Continued use of ReiBot after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
